Package edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.frc2.command

Class SynchronousPIDCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.frc2.command.SendableCommandBase
      • edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.frc2.command.SynchronousPIDCommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Command, edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.Sendable
    public class SynchronousPIDCommand
extends SendableCommandBase
    A command that controls an output with a PIDController. Runs forever by default - to add exit conditions and/or other behavior, subclass this class. The controller calculation and output are performed synchronously in the command's execute() method.
